**Project Alpha landing page deployed.**

Saved to Google Drive as **alpha.html** in your deployment folder.

**Preview URL:** https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k7GonUwIRad9mrbe5BLHZrnz9wxF50b0/view

---

**Key Features:**
- Modern gradient design (purple/blue)
- Animated hero section with "Coming Soon" badge
- Email capture form with inline success state
- Three feature cards highlighting speed, security, and UX
- Fully responsive (mobile-optimized)
- Smooth animations and hover effects
- Clean, production-ready code

Ready for FTP deployment to `skalatsky.com/Alex/alpha.html` when you confirm.

---

